tags.name: Scott Lake
tags.note: This lake was named after Joseph M. Scott. The Scott family were the first people to live close to the lake. Their land patent was granted on 1869-09-01. The lake is mentioned without a name in a land survey done on 1853-08-21 by Josiah W. Preston.
